{"tid":1544101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全部人10月1號唱香港國歌！！！《願榮光歸香港》","createTime":"2019-09-05T12:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T04:25:03.000Z","uid":174658,"like":270,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"7b1fff78b10a622317c332bb89142bdac6412526","tid":1544101,"uid":174658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:17:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWGyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=45836fc6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n終於明白點解有人會聽國歌聽到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為首歌正正代表當地既價值同信念！<br />\n諗下自己聽鄰國國歌定《願榮光歸香港》會成身震哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝製作團隊，以你們為傲"},{"pid":"f439a455fe34bc1aa42d1137eb6d2fed47a27699","tid":1544101,"uid":305794,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:17:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">［幫手推到置頂］9月8日 美領人鏈防鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544032</a><br />\n跪求各位巴絲幫手推一推<del>（我係一個有夢想既P牌仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）</del><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e399656ce22267c4a75e1e3d932662cadda71520","tid":1544101,"uid":174658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:23:40.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7453ccced75d870e745a23f3867fae9709043d89","tid":1544101,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:23:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35cbd62f2505ecdba9db515ff2468e6f520f7e3a","tid":1544101,"uid":263150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:27:50.000Z","msg":"其實改詞犯唔犯法？"},{"pid":"be9d014bb3da0939432bf95d6e0652be5d76c7bf","tid":1544101,"uid":119055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:28:12.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"72abfb7fd766b09e6f61f990d1b915e1649d808f","tid":1544101,"uid":83348,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:29:17.000Z","msg":"第三句就流淚了😭"},{"pid":"8fcaff89204f9bab47456a7ce46ca9b2e9aff233","tid":1544101,"uid":67412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:29:37.000Z","msg":"希望攪得成!努力記歌詞中!"},{"pid":"ae973ebe51952be2e5f59c3742ab4e1dfab75514","tid":1544101,"uid":174658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:31:38.000Z","msg":"如果要搞得成就要加強地區宣傳，感召多D人"},{"pid":"3ceecab01f7fed4df3a552cbe6612f9e80e3ae22","tid":1544101,"uid":318140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:31:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好正"},{"pid":"3b